column4: Please do not abbreviate your words.
I need some time to put together my answer.
What other classes can you use?
Can I add you to my friend list?
Do you want me to repair it?
Do you want to join my linkshell?
Do you want to join my free company?
Can I join your free company?
If you would be so kind.
I don't know how to answer that question.
Thanks for the offer, but I'll have to pass.
Have stuff to do, gotta go!
Can you do it for me?
I don't have anything to give you.
Just for a short time is fine.
It's better if our levels aren't too far apart.
I'm putting together a guildhest party.
My gear is in poor condition.
Please wait until weakness wears off.
